gets, the lower the corrupt gaurd faction gets.  Be weary of this when you need to hit the bank in Qeynos or turn in sashes at the paladin guild, I'm KOS with the corrupt gaurds but so far they are all green.  But, I got my Aegis finally, so I will probably never return to Qeynos anyways. <BR>Good luck fellow clerics!<BR>Martuk</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Cinina</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">How do you con to merchants?<P>If you can get yourself indifferent to merchants, you can feed Captain Rohand brandies to get yourself to warmly with the non-corrupt guards and increase your merchant faction as well.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
